1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about hand hygiene than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:07,200
Most germs thrive on our hands.

3
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:09,600
But how we wash them matters.

4
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:11,600
Simply running them under water?

5
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:12,400
Not enough!

6
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:13,600
You need soap.

7
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:17,600
Studies show washing for 20 seconds removes 99% of germs.

8
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:19,600
So sing your favorite tune!

9
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:23,600
Neglecting this can lead to illness, especially for the vulnerable.

10
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:25,200
It’s simple but vital.

11
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:27,200
So, wash your hands regularly.

12
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:29,600
Stay safe and share this knowledge!
